<div id="wPhone" class="popWrap innerPopup">	
	<div id="wSelSong">
		<div class="titConS"><h3 class="bg1">통화연결음 설정</h3></div>
		<div class="cont">
			<p>휴대폰(<strong class="fontCor01">$StringCutUtil.getFullPhoneNum("$!{command.getNumber}")</strong>)으로<br />
			<span id="certOk" #if($StringUtils.equals("$!{dto.apiResult.result}","S")) style="display:inline;" #else style="display:none;" #end>인증번호가 발송되었습니다.<br />도착한 인증번호를 입력해주세요.</span>
